<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Bloccit</h1>
  <p>Bloccit is a resource for sharing links with your friends!</p>
  <% if !current_user %>
    <p>
      <%= link_to "Sign in", new_session_path %> or
      <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %> today!
    </p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Invents new colors</h2>
    <p>Bloccit will generate colors outside of the RGB spectrum.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Generates arbitrary frequencies</h2>
    <p>Itching to hear a 415Hz sine wave? Bloccit has you covered.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Communicates with extradimensional lifeforms</h2>
    <p>Bloccit has the ability to send messages to beings including zarnaps, hygies, and jikos</p>
  </div>
</div>
    